OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report on
OL,7,FOperation Truman
OL,9,FThe peaceful, pristine suburban town
OL,10,Fof Cranbrook in East Devon - with its
OL,11,Ftree-lined streets and new-build
OL,12,Fhouses - is the last place you would
OL,13,Fexpect to be at the centre of a major
OL,14,Fcriminal conspiracy.
OL,16,FFifteen years ago, as Cranbrook was
OL,17,Fbeing developed and prepared for
OL,18,Fresidents, it needed a district
OL,19,Fheating system.
