OL,6,FTwo men - who worked for energy firm
OL,7,FE.ON - were in charge of the project,
OL,8,Fand began handing out lucrative
OL,9,Fcontracts to construction firms. As it
OL,10,Fturned out, they were accepting
OL,11,Fmillions of pounds in bribes.
OL,13,FDrugs, gambling and climbing the
