OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Dan Parkinson,
OL,7,Ffrom Devon and Cornwall Police's
OL,8,Fserious organised crime branch, told
OL,9,FITV News West Country the
OL,10,Finvestigation - codenamed Operation
OL,11,FTruman - was complex and took years to
OL,12,Ffully unravel.
OL,14,FThe pair at the centre of the case,
OL,15,FMark Baker and Matthew Heyward, along
OL,16,Fwith Mr Baker's wife, Angela, spent
OL,17,Ffour years taking huge bribes through
OL,18,Fvarious channels.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/20
