OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,FThe conspiracy came crashing down when
OL,7,FE.ON realised what was happening and
OL,8,Falerted the police.
OL,10,FOn Thursday, at Winchester Crown
OL,11,FCourt, the six were sentenced for
OL,12,Foffences including fraud, bribery and
OL,13,Fmoney laundering.
OL,15,F'They thought they were never going to
OL,16,Fget caught'
OL,18,F"When we looked at the evidence, it
OL,19,Fwas quite obvious," said DI Parkinson.
OL,20,F"I think they thought they were never
OL,21,Fgoing to get caught.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/20
