OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,F"It can be incredibly tempting as a
OL,7,Fbusiness to pay a bribe to get a
OL,8,Fcontract. But if you do it, you are
OL,9,Fcommitting an offence and perpetuating
OL,10,Fthis situation.
OL,12,F"The contracts were extremely large,
OL,13,Fand the amount in bribery totalled
OL,14,Fabout #2 million. That's the scale
OL,15,Fwe're looking at.
