OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,F"At the heart of it, this is about
OL,7,Femployees of E.ON - who should have
OL,8,Fbeen acting in the best interests of
OL,9,Fthe company - taking bribes and
OL,10,Fbackhanders and putting contractors in
OL,11,Fplace who would pay those."
OL,13,FCorrupt relationships
OL,15,FBack in 2010, Cranbrook - six miles
OL,16,Foutside Exeter - was being developed
OL,17,Fas a new town.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/20
