OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,FThese companies were construction
OL,7,Fcontractors who either had or wanted a
OL,8,Fcommercial relationship with E.ON.
OL,10,FPolice said Mark Baker's role was
OL,11,Fdeciding which companies should be
OL,12,Fgiven valuable construction contracts
OL,13,Fat Cranbrook, and later at other
OL,14,Flocations around the UK.
OL,16,FThe bribes started in 2011 and
OL,17,Fcontinued through until the end of
OL,18,F2015.
OL,20,F'It undermines how business works'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/20
