OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,F"When you talk about bribery, people
OL,7,Fthink it's just one person paying a
OL,8,Fbribe to get a contract," DI Parkinson
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"In this case, the employees at E.ON
OL,12,Fwere putting in particular contractors
OL,13,Fwho they knew would pay them bribes,
OL,14,Fand allowing them to put in inflated
OL,15,Finvoices, so the money they were
OL,16,Fgetting actually came from E.ON."
OL,18,FDI Parkinson says there are many more
OL,19,Fvictims in this case.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/20
