OL,3,CThe quiet town at the centre of a
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound criminal conspiracy
OL,6,F"There were lots of other businesses
OL,7,Fwho were bidding for work, but in
OL,8,Fhindsight they were never going to get
OL,9,Fthat work, because they were not part
OL,10,Fof this corrupt relationship," he said.
OL,12,F"It undermines how business operates
OL,13,Fand has a wider impact."
OL,15,FFake references, false invoices and
OL,16,Fwage slips and multiple house moves
OL,18,FPolice say between 2011 and 2014, Mark
OL,19,Fand Angela Baker moved house four
OL,20,Ftimes, with each of the moves "tainted
OL,21,Fby fraud".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/20
