OL,6,FIn 2012 they moved from Lincolnshire
OL,7,Fto Devon to be closer to the site in
OL,8,FCranbrook.
OL,10,FIn their rental application they
OL,11,Ffalsely declared that Angela Baker
OL,12,Fworked for RKC on an annual salary of
OL,13,F#60,000. Timothy Paterson enabled this
OL,14,Ffraud by creating a reference and fake
OL,15,Fwage slips.
OL,17,FIn 2013 the Bakers started the process
OL,18,Fof buying a house with a mortgage in
OL,19,FOkehampton.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/20
