OL,6,FRKC paid the deposit and obtained the
OL,7,Fmortgage by fraud, and paid for
OL,8,Fimprovements to the home.
OL,10,FAngela Baker told the bank she was
OL,11,Fworking for RKC on a salary of #85,000
OL,12,Fper year, with fake wage slips again
OL,13,Fcreated to disguise the fraud.
OL,15,FAfter spending some of the money on a
OL,16,Fcar and holidays, the Bakers bought a
OL,17,Fhouse in Yorkshire in late 2013.
